description.narrative: In 2019, the Social Policy section supported Countries' effort of leveraging more resources for the achievement of Key results for children in WCAR. Civil society organizations were also empowered for effective social accountability in the use of social sector resources. Capacity building in support to National social protection systems, evidence generation, data-driven advocacy, and strengthening strategic partnership in Public Finance were the focus of our work. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:08/01/2020
